OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F302A1779930189
OL,3,CStrike action does work, resident
OL,4,Cdoctors' leader says ahead of June
OL,5,Cwalkout
OL,7,FStrike action has been effective at
OL,8,Fbringing the Government to the
OL,9,Fnegotiating table in the past, the
OL,10,FBritish Medical Association (BMA) has
OL,11,Fsaid ahead of a four-day strike next
OL,12,Fmonth.
OL,14,FDr Jack Fletcher, chairman of the
OL,15,FBMA's resident doctors' committee,
OL,16,Fsaid doctors were being lost to other
OL,17,Fcountries because they are not valued,
OL,18,Fas he urged the Government to settle
OL,19,Fthe dispute.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G1/11
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,303,300,200,140,000,100
PN,30202
SC,0002
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F302A1779930189
OL,3,CStrike action does work, resident
OL,4,Cdoctors' leader says ahead of June
OL,5,Cwalkout
OL,7,FHis comments come as the BMA confirmed
OL,8,Fthat resident doctors will strike from
OL,9,F7am on Monday June 15 to 6.59am on
OL,10,FFriday June 19.
OL,12,FThe announcement followed the union's
OL,13,Ffirst talks with new Health Secretary
OL,14,FJames Murray on Wednesday, where they
OL,15,Ffailed to reach a deal on pay and job
OL,16,Fprotections.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G2/11
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,303,300,200,140,000,100
PN,30203
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F302A1779930189
OL,3,CStrike action does work, resident
OL,4,Cdoctors' leader says ahead of June
OL,5,Cwalkout
OL,7,FWhen asked if previous strikes were
OL,8,Feffective, Dr Fletcher told the Press
OL,9,FAssociation: "In response to the
OL,10,Findustrial action, I don't agree that
OL,11,Fit hasn't worked previously.
OL,13,F"In November, we wrote to the Health
OL,14,FSecretary to come to the table, he
OL,15,Fdidn't respond, and therefore we
OL,16,Fannounced industrial action which
OL,17,Fbrought him to the table. That led to
OL,18,Fa number of things, including an offer.
OL,26,@qD@NOUuD@AOU
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G3/11
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,303,300,200,140,000,100
PN,30204
SC,0004
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F302A1779930189
OL,3,CStrike action does work, resident
OL,4,Cdoctors' leader says ahead of June
OL,5,Cwalkout
OL,7,F"We put that off to our members in
OL,8,FDecember, that was rejected and then
OL,9,Fwe then took industrial action to get
OL,10,Fa better offer.
OL,12,F"We've been in discussions in January,
OL,13,FFebruary, March, and those discussions
OL,14,Fwere very constructive, however, they
OL,15,Ffundamentally didn't address the
OL,16,Fproblems that we have.
OL,18,F"We are losing doctors to other
OL,19,Fcountries because they are not valued.
OL,26,@oD@AOUtD@AOUzD@AOU
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G4/11
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,303,300,200,140,000,100
PN,30205
SC,0005
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F302A1779930189
OL,3,CStrike action does work, resident
OL,4,Cdoctors' leader says ahead of June
OL,5,Cwalkout
OL,7,F"I don't want to be taking further
OL,8,Findustrial action.
OL,10,F"I want to be getting an offer that we
OL,11,Fcan put to our members to bring this
OL,12,Fdispute to a close, but fundamentally,
OL,13,Fthat isn't going to happen if the
OL,14,FHealth Secretary and this team are not
OL,15,Fwilling to move on the previous offer."
OL,26,@oD@AOUrD@AOUwD@gO]
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G5/11
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,303,300,200,140,000,100
PN,30206
SC,0006
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F302A1779930189
OL,3,CStrike action does work, resident
OL,4,Cdoctors' leader says ahead of June
OL,5,Cwalkout
OL,7,FLast month, Sir Jim Mackey, chief
OL,8,Fexecutive of NHS England, warned
OL,9,Fhospital leaders to plan for a "long
OL,10,Fperiod of strikes" and suggested the
OL,11,FNHS would seek to become less reliant
OL,12,Fon doctors in training if disruption
OL,13,Fcontinued.
OL,15,FDr Fletcher warned moving further away
OL,16,Ffrom doctor-led care would worsen
OL,17,Fproductivity in the NHS.
OL,26,@qD@`OUrD@RO]
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G6/11
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,303,300,200,140,000,100
PN,30207
SC,0007
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F302A1779930189
OL,3,CStrike action does work, resident
OL,4,Cdoctors' leader says ahead of June
OL,5,Cwalkout
OL,7,FHe said: "For the last decade or so we
OL,8,Fhave seen dropping productivity in our
OL,9,FNHS, despite employing more and more
OL,10,Fpeople, and a move away from doctor-
OL,11,Fled care.
OL,13,F"If you're employing more people
OL,14,Fwhilst moving away from doctor-led
OL,15,Fcare, and therefore becoming less
OL,16,Fproductive, why on earth would you
OL,17,Fwant to continue that in the future?
OL,19,F"Fundamentally, we think the NHS is
OL,20,Fless productive, and NHS England
OL,21,Fagrees with that.
OL,26,@oD@JOUuD@AOU{D@AOU
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G7/11
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,303,300,200,140,000,100
PN,30208
SC,0008
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F302A1779930189
OL,3,CStrike action does work, resident
OL,4,Cdoctors' leader says ahead of June
OL,5,Cwalkout
OL,7,F"I actually think we need more
OL,8,Fdoctors. Other OECD (Organisation for
OL,9,FEconomic Co-operation and Development)
OL,10,Fcountries have higher numbers of
OL,11,Fdoctors in their healthcare systems,
OL,12,Fand they see better waiting list
OL,13,Ftimes, reduced A&E waits and improved
OL,14,Faccess to GPs.
OL,16,F"This is why I said we should go in
OL,17,Fthat direction, rather than continuing
OL,18,Fdown this journey that was started a
OL,19,Fdecade ago."
OL,26,@oD@AOUxD@AOU{D@LO]
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G8/11
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
