OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F302A1779930189
OL,3,CStrike action does work, resident
OL,4,Cdoctors' leader says ahead of June
OL,5,Cwalkout
OL,7,FMr Murray, who was appointed after the
OL,8,Fresignation of Wes Streeting earlier
OL,9,Fthis month, said he wanted a
OL,10,F"productive relationship" with the
OL,11,FBMA, but the union's demands for
OL,12,Ffurther pay increases were
OL,13,F"unrealistic, unaffordable, and
OL,14,Funsustainable".
OL,26,@rD@AOUrD@YO]uD@AOUvD@NO]
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G9/11
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,303,300,200,140,000,100
PN,30210
SC,0010
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F302A1779930189
OL,3,CStrike action does work, resident
OL,4,Cdoctors' leader says ahead of June
OL,5,Cwalkout
OL,7,FSpeaking after the strike action was
OL,8,Fannounced, he said: "I'm disappointed
OL,9,Fthat the BMA have refused to consider
OL,10,Ffurther discussions about how to
OL,11,Fstrengthen the deal on the table and
OL,12,Fhave instead rushed once again to
OL,13,Funnecessary and unreasonable strike
OL,14,Faction.
OL,26,@pD@UOU
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                   G10/11
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,303,300,200,140,000,100
PN,30211
SC,0011
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F302A1779930189
OL,3,CStrike action does work, resident
OL,4,Cdoctors' leader says ahead of June
OL,5,Cwalkout
OL,7,F"I was clear with the BMA that after a
OL,8,F33.4% pay rise for resident doctors
OL,9,Fover the last four years ` the highest
OL,10,Fanywhere across the public sector `
OL,11,Fthe BMA's demands for further
OL,12,Fsubstantial pay increases this year
OL,13,Fare unrealistic, unaffordable, and
OL,14,Funsustainable.
OL,16,F"These are simply not grounds for yet
OL,17,Fmore strike action, which patients do
OL,18,Fnot support, puts further pressure on
OL,19,Fother staff, and costs the NHS
OL,20,Fhundreds of millions of pounds."
OL,26,@oD@AOUxD@AOU|D@`O]
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                   G11/11
